      "options": "<div style='padding: 8px 0;'><h4>What is Pathfinder?</h4><p>Pathfinder is a visual field-path navigator for Frappe that lets you:</p><ul><li>Browse DocType link chains visually (e.g. PF Enrollments → PF Person → PF Family → last_name)</li><li>Create <strong>virtual fields</strong> — dot-notation paths that resolve values across linked documents at runtime</li><li>Generate <strong>Jinja tags</strong> for email/SMS/text templates (e.g. <code>{{ doc.person_id.family_id.last_name }}</code>)</li><li>Generate <strong>Frappe paths</strong> for programmatic use in custom code</li></ul></div>"
